        <div class="content">
            <div class="left-column">
                <h1>ShaktiRide: Empowering Women on the Move</h1>
                <h2>Your Safe, Trusted, Women-Only Ride Service</h2>
                <p>At ShaktiRide, we believe every woman deserves a safe and comfortable journey. Our platform connects women riders with women drivers, creating a community built on trust, security, and empowerment.</p>
                <h3>Why Choose ShaktiRide?</h3>
                <p>We prioritize your safety with verified women drivers, affordable fares, and timely rides. Whether commuting to work, attending an event, or running errands, ShaktiRide is your reliable travel companion.</p>
                <p>Together, we are driving change — one ride at a time.</p>
                <a href="#book" class="cta-button">Book Your Ride</a>
            </div>
            <div class="right-column">
    <div class="image-frame">
        <img src="/Images/women.png" alt="Driver" class="bg-image">
        <img src="/Images/womendrive.png" alt="Rider" class="circle-image">
    </div>
</div>
        </div>
    </section>

